						               													<description>A &amp;ldquo;STICK OR TWIST&amp;rdquo; GAME&amp;#10;OBJECT: to be the first to fill your pyramid with coloured blocks.&amp;#10;On your turn, you roll the dice. Depending on the colours showing on the dice, you can take (if you can place them) the corresponding coloured blocks and place them on your board. You can decide to stop there and then you will have definitively won the coloured blocks you picked up on your turn. OR, you can also decide to roll the unused dice again and try to collect more blocks. In this case, you roll again, and so on. BUT BEWARE, if on one of these subsequent dice rolls you cannot place a new block on your board, you lose ALL the blocks you collected during that turn. You win the game by being the first player to complete your pyramid.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;+++  It is important to learn to stop in time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
